('Natural Therapy Spa: From Cold Plunge to Tea Bath',
'In Jakarta, the wellness boom is manifesting in an increasing number of fluid, one-stop destinations that blend convenience with personalized care. These spaces are redefining the concept of well-being by combining traditional healing wisdom with modern approaches. Some venues emphasize the social aspect of self-care, offering communal experiences that foster a sense of connection and shared wellness journeys. Stephanie Tjiu, co-founder of Anda Wellness, highlights the growing anxiety within her generation, noting a shift in how people advocate for their own health. Anda Wellness began as a massage home service in 2020 and has since expanded into Anda Reserva, Indonesia''s first social wellness club. This evolution reflects a broader trend where individuals are delving into medical journals from various cultures to understand what best works for their bodies. As awareness grows, people are increasingly eager to build and explore wellness habits that support their overall health. Anda Reserva aims to provide a space for individuals to cultivate these habits, offering a platform for exploration and personal growth in well-being. By integrating diverse healing traditions with modern insights, Jakarta''s wellness destinations are crafting new pathways for individuals to achieve a balanced and healthy lifestyle.',
'https://res.cloudinary.com/dxjm1mdjc/image/upload/v1746945487/c1ac897f-6d8c-472e-a755-86370d57386e.png',
NULL,
'23a068f8-6759-4897-bbb0-f675e1d52dcb'),

('Zoomoov Plaza Blok M: The Land of ZOOMOOV!',
'Apakah Anda mencari cara menyenangkan untuk menghabiskan waktu bersama si kecil? Kami hadir dengan solusi menarik: persewaan robot binatang lucu. Tempat ini menyediakan berbagai jenis robot binatang yang bisa dinaiki oleh anak-anak dan satu pendamping dewasa. Dengan desain yang aman dan ergonomis, setiap robot menawarkan pengalaman berkendara yang seru dan menghibur, cocok untuk anak-anak maupun orang dewasa yang menemani. Kami menawarkan berbagai pilihan robot binatang, mulai dari gajah yang megah hingga kuda poni yang menggemaskan. Semua robot dirancang dengan perhatian khusus terhadap detail dan keamanan, memastikan setiap perjalanan menjadi kenangan indah. Tempat persewaan ini cocok untuk berbagai acara, seperti pesta ulang tahun atau sekadar menghabiskan akhir pekan bersama keluarga. Dengan harga yang terjangkau, Anda dan si kecil dapat menikmati petualangan tanpa batas dalam dunia robot binatang yang penuh warna.',
